# Environment Variables for Niyi's Portfolio

## Local Development
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in your values.
# Never commit .env.local to git.

VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://YOUR_PROJECT_ID.supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=YOUR_ANON_PUBLIC_KEY_HERE

# Contact form delivery — free key from https://web3forms.com (no signup wall, just email verification)
VITE_WEB3FORMS_KEY=YOUR_WEB3FORMS_ACCESS_KEY_HERE

## Vercel Deployment
# Add these same variables in:
# Vercel Dashboard → Your Project → Settings → Environment Variables
